"{\"uid\": \"dailyfreepress.com-03-26-21-203116-losing-the-linkedin-olympics-identity-unveiled\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"For college students in Boston, LinkedIn has evolved from a professional networking platform to a staple of everyday life.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24, \"end\": 30, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"score\": 0.9999999855845091, \"rank\": 1.4355959235233763e-08, \"text\": \"Boston\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston\"}, {\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 40, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"college students\", \"from\": 4, \"to\": 20}, {\"ngram\": \"a professional networking platform\", \"from\": 58, \"to\": 92}, {\"ngram\": \"a staple\", \"from\": 96, \"to\": 104}, {\"ngram\": \"everyday life\", \"from\": 108, \"to\": 121}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The site, founded in 2002, was created to allow business professionals to increase business connections, search for jobs and look for new hires.\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The site\", \"from\": 123, \"to\": 131}, {\"ngram\": \"business professionals\", \"from\": 171, \"to\": 193}, {\"ngram\": \"business connections\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 226}, {\"ngram\": \"search\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 234}, {\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 239, \"to\": 243}, {\"ngram\": \"new hires\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 266}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I was introduced to LinkedIn during my senior year of high school.\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 335, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LinkedIn\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"my senior year\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 319}, {\"ngram\": \"high school\", \"from\": 323, \"to\": 334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My peers described the blue and white app as an \\\"Instagram for academics.\\\"\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 410, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My peers\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"the blue and white app\", \"from\": 355, \"to\": 377}, {\"ngram\": \"an \\\"Instagram\", \"from\": 381, \"to\": 394}, {\"ngram\": \"academics\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 408}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Struggling with the changes to my school routine that COVID-19 pandemic brought on, I thought little about the platform.\", \"from\": 411, \"to\": 531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 465, \"end\": 482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"score\": 0.9999998266671505, \"rank\": 1.7214559319402943e-07, \"text\": \"COVID-19 pandemic\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/COVID-19_pandemic\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the changes\", \"from\": 427, \"to\": 438}, {\"ngram\": \"my school routine\", \"from\": 442, \"to\": 459}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 518, \"to\": 530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"As a soon-to-be first generation college student, the pressure to navigate the college application process by myself was already more than I could bear.\", \"from\": 532, \"to\": 684, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a soon-to-be first generation college student\", \"from\": 535, \"to\": 580}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 594}, {\"ngram\": \"the college application process\", \"from\": 607, \"to\": 638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Upon entering Boston University, I immediately scrambled to catch up to my seemingly more knowledgeable peers.\", \"from\": 686, \"to\": 796, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 700, \"end\": 717, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999998904059, \"rank\": 1.0944659903669875e-10, \"text\": \"Boston University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my seemingly more knowledgeable peers\", \"from\": 758, \"to\": 795}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In a city with some of the most prestigious universities in the world, I took the first step to \\\"fit in\\\" by creating a LinkedIn account.\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 933, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 916, \"end\": 924, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a city\", \"from\": 800, \"to\": 806}, {\"ngram\": \"the most prestigious universities\", \"from\": 820, \"to\": 853}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 857, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"the first step\", \"from\": 875, \"to\": 889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I recall devoting an unreasonable amount of time to curate the perfect profile.\", \"from\": 935, \"to\": 1014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an unreasonable amount\", \"from\": 953, \"to\": 975}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 979, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"the perfect profile\", \"from\": 994, \"to\": 1013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I rummaged through the internet for LinkedIn tips in a desperate attempt to exaggerate my lackluster resume.\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1123, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1051, \"end\": 1059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the internet\", \"from\": 1034, \"to\": 1046}, {\"ngram\": \"a desperate attempt\", \"from\": 1068, \"to\": 1087}, {\"ngram\": \"my lackluster resume\", \"from\": 1102, \"to\": 1122}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I wondered if recruiters could tell that my headshot was a zoomed-in group photo of me with a blouse edited in, and that's the reason why they did not respond to my cold message.\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1302, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"recruiters\", \"from\": 1138, \"to\": 1148}, {\"ngram\": \"my headshot\", \"from\": 1165, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"a zoomed-in group photo\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1204}, {\"ngram\": \"a blouse\", \"from\": 1216, \"to\": 1224}, {\"ngram\": \"the reason\", \"from\": 1247, \"to\": 1257}, {\"ngram\": \"my cold message\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1301}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Throughout the course of my undergraduate career, my connections grew steadily, but my activity on LinkedIn gradually declined in turn.\", \"from\": 1304, \"to\": 1439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1403, \"end\": 1411, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the course\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"my undergraduate career\", \"from\": 1329, \"to\": 1352}, {\"ngram\": \"my connections\", \"from\": 1354, \"to\": 1368}, {\"ngram\": \"my activity\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1399}, {\"ngram\": \"turn\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I found myself burdened with the weight of my acquaintances' impressive achievements whenever I scrolled through the app.\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1561, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the weight\", \"from\": 1469, \"to\": 1479}, {\"ngram\": \"my acquaintances' impressive achievements\", \"from\": 1483, \"to\": 1524}, {\"ngram\": \"the app\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1560}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be honest, I do not even know half of my connections personally - I am willing to bet that most college students with 500 plus connections do not either.\", \"from\": 1563, \"to\": 1719, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"half\", \"from\": 1596, \"to\": 1600}, {\"ngram\": \"my connections\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1618}, {\"ngram\": \"most college students\", \"from\": 1657, \"to\": 1678}, {\"ngram\": \"500 plus connections\", \"from\": 1684, \"to\": 1704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Think of it this way: a person would never openly brag about their accomplishments to strangers they have never met, much less announce it to everyone within ears reach.\", \"from\": 1721, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a person\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1751}, {\"ngram\": \"their accomplishments\", \"from\": 1782, \"to\": 1803}, {\"ngram\": \"strangers\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1816}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1863, \"to\": 1871}, {\"ngram\": \"ears\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1883}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LinkedIn normalizes just that, as the platform literally has a built-in notification option for sharing any updates with all existing connections.\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 2037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LinkedIn\", \"from\": 1891, \"to\": 1899}, {\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 1925, \"to\": 1937}, {\"ngram\": \"a built-in notification option\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1982}, {\"ngram\": \"any updates\", \"from\": 1995, \"to\": 2006}, {\"ngram\": \"all existing connections\", \"from\": 2012, \"to\": 2036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LinkedIn mirrors every other social media platform in setting a stage for comparison.\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"LinkedIn mirrors\", \"from\": 2039, \"to\": 2055}, {\"ngram\": \"every other social media platform\", \"from\": 2056, \"to\": 2089}, {\"ngram\": \"a stage\", \"from\": 2101, \"to\": 2108}, {\"ngram\": \"comparison\", \"from\": 2113, \"to\": 2123}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead of admiring an influencer's lifestyle on Instagram, I hyperfixate on my peers' career accomplishments on LinkedIn.\", \"from\": 2125, \"to\": 2247, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2174, \"end\": 2183, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.521815315362938e-33, \"text\": \"Instagram\", \"types\": [\"Q7397\", \"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Instagram\"}, {\"begin\": 2238, \"end\": 2246, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an influencer's lifestyle\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2170}, {\"ngram\": \"my peers' career accomplishments\", \"from\": 2202, \"to\": 2234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I compare myself to them through internship experience and GPA, and pay the price with my peace of mind.\", \"from\": 2248, \"to\": 2352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2307, \"end\": 2310, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.3655098001629994e-12, \"text\": \"GPA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Grading_in_education\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"internship experience\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2302}, {\"ngram\": \"the price\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2329}, {\"ngram\": \"my peace\", \"from\": 2335, \"to\": 2343}, {\"ngram\": \"mind\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2351}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My insecurities are amplified - and I feel obligated to keep it to myself.\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2427, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My insecurities\", \"from\": 2353, \"to\": 2368}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The LinkedIn community demands positivity and support, so feeling bitter about a peer's achievements breaks an unspoken code of professionalism.\", \"from\": 2429, \"to\": 2573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2433, \"end\": 2441, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"positivity\", \"from\": 2460, \"to\": 2470}, {\"ngram\": \"support\", \"from\": 2475, \"to\": 2482}, {\"ngram\": \"a peer's achievements\", \"from\": 2508, \"to\": 2529}, {\"ngram\": \"an unspoken code\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2553}, {\"ngram\": \"professionalism\", \"from\": 2557, \"to\": 2572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The irony lies in the fact that by being a part of the LinkedIn community, individuals are inadvertently contributing to the same environment that fosters feelings of jealousy and inadequacy for themselves.\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2780, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2629, \"end\": 2637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The irony\", \"from\": 2574, \"to\": 2583}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 2592, \"to\": 2600}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2621}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2660}, {\"ngram\": \"the same environment\", \"from\": 2695, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"feelings\", \"from\": 2729, \"to\": 2737}, {\"ngram\": \"jealousy\", \"from\": 2741, \"to\": 2749}, {\"ngram\": \"inadequacy\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2764}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Especially for first-generation college students battling imposter syndrome, LinkedIn can be alienating.\", \"from\": 2781, \"to\": 2885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2858, \"end\": 2866, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"first-generation college students\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"imposter syndrome\", \"from\": 2839, \"to\": 2856}]}, {\"sentence\": \"LinkedIn's promotion of hustle culture is a capitalist's ultimate fantasy.\", \"from\": 2887, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2887, \"end\": 2895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hustle culture\", \"from\": 2911, \"to\": 2925}, {\"ngram\": \"a capitalist's ultimate fantasy\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pervasive \\\"rise and grind\\\" mentality that one must only devote themselves to work and sacrifice everything outside of it exists to pressure people into tying their self-worth to their career pursuits.\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3166, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The pervasive \\\"rise and grind\\\" mentality\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 3002}, {\"ngram\": \"one\", \"from\": 3008, \"to\": 3011}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3072}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 3106, \"to\": 3112}, {\"ngram\": \"their career pursuits\", \"from\": 3144, \"to\": 3165}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It feels as though hobbies that do not align with career ambitions are worthless and any leisure time should be utilized to work even harder.\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3309, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hobbies\", \"from\": 3187, \"to\": 3194}, {\"ngram\": \"career ambitions\", \"from\": 3218, \"to\": 3234}, {\"ngram\": \"any leisure time\", \"from\": 3253, \"to\": 3269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A relentless fixation on productivity only pushes us to become soulless machines.\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3391, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A relentless fixation\", \"from\": 3310, \"to\": 3331}, {\"ngram\": \"productivity\", \"from\": 3335, \"to\": 3347}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3360, \"to\": 3362}, {\"ngram\": \"soulless machines\", \"from\": 3373, \"to\": 3390}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no winning the LinkedIn Olympics, yet we still try.\", \"from\": 3393, \"to\": 3453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3417, \"end\": 3425, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"LinkedIn\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/LinkedIn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It's crucial to understand that success should not come at the expense of someone's mental well-being.\", \"from\": 3455, \"to\": 3557, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 3487, \"to\": 3494}, {\"ngram\": \"the expense\", \"from\": 3514, \"to\": 3525}, {\"ngram\": \"someone's mental well-being\", \"from\": 3529, \"to\": 3556}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is important to concentrate on genuine personal improvement rather than being engrossed in endless comparison.\", \"from\": 3558, \"to\": 3671, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"genuine personal improvement\", \"from\": 3592, \"to\": 3620}, {\"ngram\": \"endless comparison\", \"from\": 3652, \"to\": 3670}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is no one-size-fits-all recipe for success - a personal balance is key.\", \"from\": 3672, \"to\": 3749, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no one-size-fits-all recipe\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3708}, {\"ngram\": \"success\", \"from\": 3713, \"to\": 3720}, {\"ngram\": \"a personal balance\", \"from\": 3723, \"to\": 3741}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your donation will support the student journalists of Boston University.\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3823, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3822, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\", \"score\": 0.9999999998904059, \"rank\": 1.0944659903669875e-10, \"text\": \"Boston University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boston_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your donation\", \"from\": 3751, \"to\": 3764}, {\"ngram\": \"the student journalists\", \"from\": 3778, \"to\": 3801}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your contribution will allow us to purchase equipment and cover our annual website hosting costs.\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3921, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your contribution\", \"from\": 3824, \"to\": 3841}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3853, \"to\": 3855}, {\"ngram\": \"equipment\", \"from\": 3868, \"to\": 3877}, {\"ngram\": \"our annual website\", \"from\": 3888, \"to\": 3906}, {\"ngram\": \"costs\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3920}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cancel reply Your email address will not be published.Required fields are marked* Comment* Name* Email*\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 4030, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Cancel\", \"from\": 3923, \"to\": 3929}, {\"ngram\": \"Your email address\", \"from\": 3936, \"to\": 3954}, {\"ngram\": \"Required fields\", \"from\": 3977, \"to\": 3992}]}]}"